request.html:
data [required]

object

Data wrapper for SAML preferences update.

attributes [required]

object

Attributes for updating SAML preferences.

default_role_uuids [required]

[string]

List of role UUIDs to assign to JIT-provisioned users. Exactly 1 role is required.

jit_domains [required]

[string]

List of domains for Just-In-Time user provisioning. Maximum 50 domains. Each domain must be between 1 and 256 characters.

type [required]

enum

Type of the resource. Allowed enum values: saml_preferences
